name: Exuberance No. 4 Yellow and Bubble Gum
description:
An extraordinary design, Exuberance No. 4 Yellow and Bubble Gum gathers inspiration from the stars and shines brightly.
Exuberance No. 4 Yellow and Bubble Gum is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
